# Autobas to Fortnox

This Chrome extension allows you to easily transfer cart data from Autobas to Fortnox. It offers one free transfer per day and unlimited transfers for subscribed users.

## Features

- Extract cart data from Autobas
- Import cart data into Fortnox
- One free transfer per day
- Unlimited transfers for subscribed users

## Installation

1. Download the extension from the Chrome Web Store
2. Click on "Add to Chrome" to install the extension

## Usage

1. On the Autobas page, click the "Spara till Fortnox" button to save your cart data
2. Navigate to your Fortnox page
3. Click the "Importera fr√•n Autobas" button to fill in the Fortnox form with your saved cart data

## Subscription

To get unlimited transfers:

1. Click the "Subscribe for Unlimited Transfers" button on the Fortnox page
2. Complete the payment process on the ExtensionPay page
